HEADWORD: Oregon grape
<hw>Or"e*gon grape`</hw> <pr>(⟦ocr⟧r"⟦esl⟧*g⟦ocr⟧n gr⟦amac⟧p`)</pr>.
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An evergreen species of barberry (<spn>Berberis
Aquifolium</spn>), of Oregon and California; also, its roundish,
blue-black berries.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

